   Politics &amp; Policy:
   Senate Panel Targets `Circle of Poison'
   As It Votes to Ban Some Pesticide Exports
   ----
   By Bruce Ingersoll
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/07/90
</DATE>
